                            <p style="text-align:left;font-size:13px; color:#0000FF; font-weight: bold;">
            
Students
                 </p>

The students admitted in the Eastern University come with a very good academic background. So far, 11,793 students were admitted into different programs till Fall 2013. Out of these about 3000 have graduated. Other students are at various stages of their studies.
<br />
<br />
                            <p style="text-align:left;font-size:13px; color:#0000FF; font-weight: bold;">
            
Faculty Members
                 </p>

Eastern University hires top-of-the class, talented graduates as junior faculty, experienced teachers and researchers as senior faculty and professionally accomplished teachers and experts as part-time faculty. As of Fall 2013, the University has over 100 fulltime faculty members. In addition, there are 55 part-time faculty members including visiting professor from USA and other countries.
<br />
                            <p style="text-align:left;font-size:13px; color:#0000FF; font-weight: bold;">

Campus
                 </p>

The University campus is located in the prime area of Dhanmandi and is easily accessible from any part of Dhaka and outskirts by public transportation as well as taxi cab, auto-rickshaw and rickshaw. 

